name: ¡Mucha Lucha! Mascaritas of the Lost Code
overview: Mucha Lucha, the over-the-top comedy TV adventure series that revolves around Lucha Libre (Mexican professional wrestling) on the Kids WB, comes to the Game Boy Advance. Wrestle your was a Rikochet, Buena Girl and the Flea through this wacky adventure in the quest to recover the all-important Code of Masked Wrestling!
